show.description: After a late-night rescue by her brother’s intense best friend Vivaan, headstrong MBA student Aanya finds herself tangled between college popularity games and raw, unexpected emotions. When her private diary is exposed at her own party, humiliation follows — until Vivaan steps in, shaking up everything she thought she knew about trust, friendship, and desire.
